Local setup

project_dir
|_grav-admin
| |_user (symlink)
|_user  
| |_grav-theme (symlink)
|_grav-theme

SYMLINKS

Webroot to Grav install
mklink /D D:\Dev\xampp\htdocs\davidraymond D:\Dev\_PROJECTS\davidraymond\grav-admin

Grav-admin user folder to project user
mklink /D D:\Dev\_PROJECTS\davidraymond\grav-admin\user D:\Dev\_PROJECTS\davidraymond\user

user/themes/project-theme to grav-theme-name
mklink /D D:\Dev\_PROJECTS\davidraymond\user\themes\davidraymond D:\Dev\_PROJECTS\davidraymond\grav-theme-davidraymond
